highlights.text: “Chop Suey!” by System Of A Down is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Canada, up 72 spots at #128.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Canada. “Tears” is the highest at #2.
“Something in the Orange” by Zach Bryan has been on Top Songs Canada the longest, at 983 days straight.
“Ordinary (feat. Luke Combs) - Live from Lollapalooza” by Alex Warren and Luke Combs is the highest new entry on Top Songs Canada at #197.
